block content
  h2#about-header What is this?

  p.about-content
   |The purpose of this project is to demonstrate how to use an express server with a database and
   |server-side rendering.<br>Here MongoDB is used as a database provided via MongoDB Atlas.
   |<br>The following technology stack is used:
  
  ul.about-list
    li Express server with NodeJS
    li Serverside rendering via PugJS template engine
    li MongoDB database synchronization via mongoose
    li Dynamic background rendered on the clientside via HTML5 canvas
    li Rate limitation, request compression and form validation checks
    li Written in Typescript

